WEBVTT

00:00:16.290 --> 00:00:17.410
Ging?

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:46.000
Chairman x And x Release

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:48.750
Yo.

00:01:52.410 --> 00:01:52.970
Ging!

00:01:56.620 --> 00:01:58.030
I'm sorry!

00:01:58.030 --> 00:01:59.510
It was my fault...

00:01:59.670 --> 00:02:01.770
Because of me, Kite

00:02:01.770 --> 00:02:04.020
turned into a little girl!

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:09.020
I h-heard he was captured by the enemy.

00:02:09.020 --> 00:02:11.560
Yeah, I was with Kite...

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.030
Then Kite told me to run away,

00:02:13.030 --> 00:02:14.280
and Pitou showed up.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:17.470
Kite lost his arm, I was knocked out,

00:02:17.470 --> 00:02:19.210
and then we trained...

00:02:19.210 --> 00:02:22.750
Shoot got Kite out of the Ants' nest,

00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:25.540
but it wasn't Kite...

00:02:26.090 --> 00:02:31.050
They did all kinds of horrible things!

00:02:34.370 --> 00:02:37.210
When I met Pitou again,

00:02:37.970 --> 00:02:41.560
Pitou said that Kite was already dead!

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:43.350
Okay, I get it!

00:02:43.350 --> 00:02:46.440
Well, I don't get it, but just have a seat, okay?

00:02:46.950 --> 00:02:49.410
U-Uh... Er...

00:02:49.410 --> 00:02:50.680
Let's calm down.

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:52.820
We should both try to calm down...

00:02:53.150 --> 00:02:56.560
It was because I insisted...

00:02:57.150 --> 00:02:59.320
on having my way!

00:02:59.540 --> 00:03:00.650
Oh, um...

00:03:00.650 --> 00:03:02.060
A-A-Anyway...

00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:03.580
Just calm down first.

00:03:04.030 --> 00:03:05.520
Ging is...

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:08.330
Ging is actually flustered.

00:03:09.070 --> 00:03:10.370
I should have

00:03:10.370 --> 00:03:12.840
been the one who died!

00:03:14.670 --> 00:03:15.700
Gon.

00:03:16.450 --> 00:03:17.710
That isn't true.

00:03:18.830 --> 00:03:23.220
He took you along because he believed in you.

00:03:24.450 --> 00:03:29.350
He told you to run because he'd
underestimated the enemy.

00:03:30.920 --> 00:03:32.950
If he hadn't thought you capable,

00:03:32.950 --> 00:03:36.360
he wouldn't have let you accompany
him, no matter what you'd said.

00:03:37.420 --> 00:03:39.990
It was his fault that he misjudged the enemy.

00:03:39.990 --> 00:03:40.920
But—

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:41.890
I know.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.470
You're also at fault for being too weak!

00:03:45.270 --> 00:03:47.500
You should feel responsible.

00:03:48.750 --> 00:03:50.430
Don't make the same mistake.

00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:54.440
And you should apologize to Kite, not to me!

00:03:55.490 --> 00:03:59.280
You didn't clearly say if he's dead or alive,

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.640
but either way, you should apologize!

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.150
Yeah.

00:04:03.550 --> 00:04:05.890
When apologizing to a friend, there's a rule.

00:04:06.290 --> 00:04:07.330
Do you know it?

00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:08.200
Huh?

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:10.140
No, what is it?

00:04:10.610 --> 00:04:14.170
You promise to do things differently next time.

00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:17.150
And you keep that promise, no matter what.

00:04:18.810 --> 00:04:19.710
Uh-huh.

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:21.820
Okay, get going!

00:04:21.820 --> 00:04:22.620
Yeah!

00:04:26.550 --> 00:04:27.160
Ging?

00:04:29.290 --> 00:04:30.370
Can I...

00:04:30.790 --> 00:04:33.670
talk to you some more later?

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:37.410
That might be difficult.

00:04:37.410 --> 00:04:39.170
I'm a busy man...

00:04:39.430 --> 00:04:41.180
That's crap, Ging!

00:04:41.180 --> 00:04:43.240
Aren't you his father?

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:45.650
How cold can you be?!

00:04:45.650 --> 00:04:48.030
I know about Greed Island!

00:04:48.030 --> 00:04:50.090
You never went to see Gon after he cleared it!

00:04:50.090 --> 00:04:51.440
Too bashful or something?

00:04:54.010 --> 00:04:55.520
All you you, shut up!

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:56.810
It's none of your business!

00:04:56.810 --> 00:04:58.070
You're a jerk, Ging!

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.460
You should apologize to Gon!

00:05:00.460 --> 00:05:03.710
Promise him you'll act more like a father!

00:05:03.710 --> 00:05:06.370
Hell, you don't have the right
to say you're his father!

00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:07.580
Make up your minds!

00:05:07.580 --> 00:05:09.080
You can all screw yourselves!

00:05:09.310 --> 00:05:12.150
You should have Leorio punch you again!

00:05:12.780 --> 00:05:14.130
Yeah, just shut up!

00:05:14.130 --> 00:05:15.450
Fine, then...

00:05:15.450 --> 00:05:17.960
I'll be waiting, so get going!

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:19.710
How stupid do you think we are?

00:05:19.710 --> 00:05:21.250
You take him there!

00:05:21.250 --> 00:05:23.350
Aren't you his father?

00:05:23.350 --> 00:05:24.870
Okay, fine!

00:05:25.220 --> 00:05:26.600
I'll take you all on!

00:05:26.900 --> 00:05:29.600
If you have a problem with
what I'm doing, bring it on!

00:05:30.540 --> 00:05:32.690
You're all against me? Okay!

00:05:32.690 --> 00:05:34.420
That's fine by me!

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:40.850
Everyone!

00:05:41.090 --> 00:05:43.890
Quiet down!

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:49.620
The election isn't over yet.

00:05:50.300 --> 00:05:53.620
Yes, I still haven't given up.

00:05:54.830 --> 00:05:57.270
A new last chance has appeared!

00:05:58.910 --> 00:05:59.490
Gon-kun—

00:05:59.490 --> 00:06:01.040
Go ahead, then.

00:06:01.910 --> 00:06:06.640
Due to the circumstances, no one
can leave until the election is over.

00:06:07.110 --> 00:06:09.440
You're in a hurry, aren't you?

00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:13.510
But this will be the final vote.

00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:15.900
Once you vote, you'll be allowed to leave.

00:06:16.450 --> 00:06:18.620
If you tell us your choice right now,

00:06:18.620 --> 00:06:22.400
everyone here will accept that as a valid vote.

00:06:26.570 --> 00:06:29.310
Between myself, Pariston, and Leorio-san,

00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:31.910
whom do you believe is most
fit to become chairman?

00:06:32.610 --> 00:06:34.550
I should mention that the
former chairman, Netero,

00:06:34.550 --> 00:06:38.170
is taking an extended vacation
after defeating the Ant King.

00:06:39.150 --> 00:06:42.400
How can you say such a thing?

00:06:43.060 --> 00:06:46.770
If Gon picks Leorio after his dramatic arrival,

00:06:46.770 --> 00:06:49.700
everyone may get caught up in
the heat of the moment again

00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:52.100
and vote for Leorio.

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.740
Chairman?

00:06:54.740 --> 00:06:56.490
Leorio's running for chairman?

00:06:56.850 --> 00:06:59.450
No! See, some stuff happened...

00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:01.190
Gon-kun,

00:07:01.940 --> 00:07:03.980
you can rely on your gut.

00:07:03.980 --> 00:07:06.450
Be true to your heart,

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:08.870
and pick one of us.

00:07:11.780 --> 00:07:14.620
Uh... Then,

00:07:15.430 --> 00:07:16.850
I'll pick Pariston-san!

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:19.330
Huh?

00:07:20.410 --> 00:07:23.630
Isn't Leorio-san your friend?

00:07:23.950 --> 00:07:27.010
Shouldn't you pick him?

00:07:27.290 --> 00:07:30.650
Nope, because Leorio wants
to become a doctor,

00:07:30.650 --> 00:07:32.100
so he can't be chairman!

00:07:36.350 --> 00:07:37.950
Of course!

00:07:39.730 --> 00:07:42.330
Now I've been completely defeated.

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:45.290
Thank you, Gon-kun.

00:07:45.770 --> 00:07:48.660
Then let's begin the vote.

00:07:48.830 --> 00:07:50.290
Oh, sorry.

00:07:50.290 --> 00:07:51.750
I'm going with Gon.

00:07:52.200 --> 00:07:54.220
My vote goes to Pariston.

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:56.590
Leorio...

00:07:56.930 --> 00:07:58.170
I know.

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:00.760
Ging!

00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:05.670
I'm going now!

00:08:07.860 --> 00:08:08.680
Yeah.

00:08:11.070 --> 00:08:13.170
Is that all you have to say, you idiot?

00:08:13.170 --> 00:08:14.700
At least say, "See you later"!

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:15.830
Where's your common sense?

00:08:17.090 --> 00:08:18.180
Ging's snapped!

00:08:18.860 --> 00:08:21.900
Someone stop this negligent jerk of a father!

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:25.070
Heart Is Valuable

00:08:22.280 --> 00:08:23.480
That's impossible!

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:26.000
Zodiacs, don't just stand there
and smile! Do something!

00:08:28.630 --> 00:08:31.070
I guess, in his own way, Ging's popular.

00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:33.590
Yeah, I guess so...

00:08:33.590 --> 00:08:34.510
Hey, Gon!

00:08:35.560 --> 00:08:36.830
I remembered something.

00:08:37.430 --> 00:08:40.280
I'm the one who taught Kite how to use <i>Nen</i>.

00:08:40.280 --> 00:08:41.460
And I taught him his techniques.

00:08:42.100 --> 00:08:47.990
There's a number that his
Crazy Slots won't bring up unless

00:08:48.630 --> 00:08:50.220
he's adamant about not dying!

00:08:51.730 --> 00:08:55.380
If he's still alive, that's probably why.

00:08:56.660 --> 00:09:01.450
He would never consider dying in your place.

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:04.480
So don't mess up your apology.

00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:07.230
Or he'll smack you again!

00:09:10.040 --> 00:09:11.240
Got it!

00:09:11.590 --> 00:09:12.880
I'm off, then!

00:09:13.370 --> 00:09:15.300
Yeah! I'll be waiting!

00:09:20.900 --> 00:09:21.920
Again?

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.010
Ging...

00:09:36.010 --> 00:09:39.270
Ninth Election for the 13th Chairman
Total Number of Hunters: 635
1) Pariston 458 (72.1%)
2) Leorio 157
